This paper deals with scene modeling using Boltzmann Machines, which is a popular technique in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of relations and affordances in the model, which are important concepts in robotics (cs.RO) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, and cs.CL.
